divs: Sighting DetailsHas anyone seen the perfect x in the sky on Feb 9th 2012, with a bright light in the middle of the x. this was so large that my daughter seen it also 86 miles away, It was to perfect to be a cloud
Summary: there was a perfect cloud shaped like the letter x very large and bright, with a bright light in the middle. was driving on kings hwy around 10:30 pm on Feb 9th 2012 with my sister. Called my daughter who lives 86miles away she seen it to
